This repository vendors a reduced header-only subset of fmt 11.1.4.

Retained files:
- include/fmt/base.h
- include/fmt/format.h
- include/fmt/format-inl.h
- LICENSE

Reason:
- `android/app/src/main/cpp/nativeui/ui_format.cpp` only uses `fmt::format`.
- The Android native UI target builds fmt in header-only mode via `FMT_HEADER_ONLY`.
- The wider fmt header set is intentionally omitted to keep the vendored surface small.

If future code starts using additional fmt facilities, add only the required headers
instead of restoring the full upstream tree.
